    <p class="description">Brighten a loved ones day with a beautiful basket bouquet arranged in a decorative basket, offering a charming and whimsical touch.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Create an elegant basket bouquet featuring a delightful mix of roses, lilies, daisies, sunflowers, and tulips. Choose from a variety of beautifully crafted baskets to complement your arrangement. Each bouquet comes with a personalized, heartfelt message card</li>
        <li>Our luxurious basket bouquets range from R 2 500 to R 4 000, depending on the flowers and basket chosen. Perfect for the special person in your life, each bespoke arrangement is crafted to exude elegance and charm, making every moment unforgettable.</li>
    </ul>
